		<Placemark id="06B550FBFE3F2C0923E1">
			<name>Jerusalem/ Church of the Holy Sepulchre</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<bettercanvas-portal style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></bettercanvas-portal><div>The polos stopped here after arriving in the Middle East to secure an amount of holy oil from the Church of the Holy Sepulchre at the request of Kublai Khan for his mother, before proceeding back through Acre to Ayas (Polo and Latham, <i>The Travels of Marco Polo</i>, 34, 36).<br></div>]]></description>
			<LookAt>
				<longitude>35.2296002</longitude>
				<latitude>31.7784813</latitude>
				<altitude>0</altitude>
				<heading>0</heading>
				<tilt>0</tilt>
				<gx:fovy>35</gx:fovy>
				<range>882.0152939108804</range>
				<altitudeMode>relativeToGround</altitudeMode>
			</LookAt>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_09BEC7D9193F6294FB41</styleUrl>
			<gx:Carousel>
				<gx:Image kml:id="hosted_image_">
					<gx:imageUrl>https://earth.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/e/*/4AE5a_Gy8-frznOpUWkTvel_JERRDu_2rLwngykGU20IDC0oyoz_7V3a3DJI96PhgadVVVHg7lBJ8kb67f-dGAX4XCqXfjF84E5mgUFhVUEE7Hvefj7Gkvg9v7mepBQlUqRPvtJDs9HQRDMctUnSiZToeO97bKbXhoWV3JZyGE0YLvPGWl3ryG5JKL3XBbP4e5FmMVensHKqgA83hgkZBDsi3eIfdBvD_avzRsqw4RljVa2-Joxxj-rdnZcWOSIIbnjOHzID2pmirNP3Xowc?authuser=0&amp;fife=s{size}</gx:imageUrl>
				</gx:Image>
			</gx:Carousel>
