			</LookAt>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_05122073C63F6294FB47</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<altitudeMode>relativeToGround</altitudeMode>
				<coordinates>44.2990761,39.70243929999999,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
	</Folder>
	<Folder id="02E28908F63F44046128">
		<name>(1277-1279) Diplomatic mission to Bagan</name>
		<open>1</open>
		<description><![CDATA[<bettercanvas-portal style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></bettercanvas-portal><div><span></span>This route marks the path recorded by Marco Polo on a diplomatic mission to the kingdom of Pagan (Marco Polo and R. E. Latham, <i>The Travels of Marco Polo</i>, Repr, Penguin Classics Harmondsworth [etc.]: Penguin, 1978), 163).<br></div><div><br></div><div>(Chapter 4)<br></div><div><br></div><div><div>Polo, Marco, and R. E. Latham. <i>The Travels of Marco Polo</i>. Repr. Penguin Classics. Harmondsworth [etc.]: Penguin, 1978.<br></div></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<styleUrl>#__managed_style_1D7FDEF4043F6294FB3F</styleUrl>
