	<Folder id="0CA915B19A3F44055D3C">
		<name>(1280s) Journeys through China</name>
		<open>1</open>
		<description><![CDATA[<div><span></span>The narrative of the source weaves through many notable cities of China, which Polo may have revisited throughout his time at the Khan's court, meaning an exact route is indeterminable<br></div><div><br></div><div>(Chapters 5-6)<br></div>]]></description>
