		<Placemark id="03E0FA2F123F2574DFE4">
			<name>Kinsai/Hangzhou</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<bettercanvas-portal style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></bettercanvas-portal><div><span style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></span><br></div><div><span style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></span><br></div><div><span style="overflow: visible; position: relative; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block;"></span><br></div><div>The 'City of Heaven' that bears an extensive canal system and over 6,000 bridges (p. 212-229)<br></div>]]></description>
