		<Placemark id="07255244E63F346073D8">
			<name>Quanzhou/ Zaiton</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<div><span></span>The port from which the Polo family is finally allowed to depart the Yuan Khanate back westward in 1292 at the Khan’s order to escort princess Kokachin to the Ilkhanate through the straits of Malaca and Hormuz (Polo and Latham, <i>The Travels of Marco Polo</i>, 43, 281).<br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
